{"type": "article", "id": 9887, "title": "New Botany 3D 限量版书籍", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-22T07:26:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052356047Xzt2yPAnLdRM6Jb.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t来自华沙的艺术家 Bozka Rydlewska 创作了一个叫做 “New Botany” 的系列 3D 立体限量版书籍。对于植物的热爱源自她童年的记忆。经过长时间的精耕细作，她运用 1：1 的比例模型把植物园中的景象用 3D 立体的形式展现在了我们面前。<a href=\"http://bozka.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是作者的个人网站</a>，点击可以查看她跟多作品，同时可以直接联系她沟通购买事宜。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235600f6Bh0oePVdYWNjnH.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235601mMkGnpJoLe4gTqWt.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235602AqlZ3GE8u9OY57Cb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235602ZWwRJOFKsDN0fGvE.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052356033d1JxfEiwy2CMFac.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235603rQmJMbeKlXYjBwt1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}